Flow Understanding:

Enterprise Level initiates clinical workflow (orders in Epic)
Department Level coordinates cardiology work (CVIS manages scheduling, reporting)
Modality Level acquires clinical data (machines generate images/measurements)
Standards Layer coordinates everything (HL7/DICOM/IHE enable data movement)

Consultant Benefit: Universal mental model for assessing any cardiology IT environment. Identify gaps systematically.

