Assessment Questions
Use these diagnostic questions with clients:

Clinical Complexity: "How many cath procedures/year? EP ablations? Advanced imaging?"
Enterprise Maturity: "When did you implement Epic? How mature is current implementation?"
IT Bandwidth: "Can your IT team maintain interfaces? What's your interface staffing?"
Registry Participation: "Are you required to report to NCDR? What's your data quality?"
Pain Points: "Show me current workflows‚Äîwhere are the manual workarounds?"

Consultant Insight: Recommendation depends on organizational context, not just technical capabilities.

üîå Standards-Based Integration: How Data Flows
Echo Workflow: Complete Data Journey
mermaidsequenceDiagram
    participant Clinician as Clinician
    participant EHR as Epic EHR
    participant CVIS as CVIS/PACS
    participant Modality as Echo Machine
    participant Reporting as Report Engine
    
    Clinician->>EHR: Orders echo exam
    
    EHR->>CVIS: HL7 ORM (Order Message)
    
    CVIS->>CVIS: Schedules procedure<br/>Creates worklist
    
    Modality->>CVIS: Queries DICOM MWL<br/>(Worklist)
    
    CVIS-->>Modality: Returns patient demographics<br/>Clinical indication
    
    Note over Modality: Tech performs ultrasound<br/>Captures measurements & images
    
    Modality->>CVIS: DICOM MPPS<br/>(Status: COMPLETE)
    
    CVIS->>Reporting: Generate structured report
    
    Note over Reporting: Encode measurements<br/>DICOM SR format<br/>with LOINC codes
    
    Reporting->>EHR: HL7 ORU (Results)<br/>Discrete measurements
    
    EHR->>EHR: CDS Alert triggered<br/>if EF ‚â§35%
    
    EHR-->>Clinician: Report in inbox<br/>CDS guidance available
Standards Reference
StandardPurposeCardiology UseHL7 v2.xText-based messagingPatient data, orders, resultsDICOMMedical imaging data/workflowMWL, Storage, MPPS, Structured ReportsIHE CATHCath workflow coordinationEmergency procedures, worklist managementIHE ECHOEcho workflow coordinationIntermittent connections, multi-stage examsHL7 FHIRModern RESTful APIFuture interoperability, ONC mandate
Key Insight: Each standard solves specific problem. Together, they create seamless workflow.

